#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:1
msgid "Git API"
msgstr "Git API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:3
msgid "Git repository helpers are available under `ptool.git` and `p.git`."
msgstr "Git 仓库辅助能力位于 `ptool.git` 和 `p.git` 下。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:5
msgid "This module is backed by `git2` / `libgit2`, not by invoking the `git` command-line tool."
msgstr "这个模块基于 `git2` / `libgit2`，而不是通过调用 `git` 命令行工具实现。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:8
msgid "Mutating operations such as `ptool.git.clone(...)`, `repo:add(...)`, `repo:commit(...)`, `repo:checkout(...)`, `repo:switch(...)`, `repo:fetch(...)`, and `repo:push(...)` accept `confirm = true` in their options table to ask the user for confirmation before the action runs."
msgstr "像 `ptool.git.clone(...)`、`repo:add(...)`、`repo:commit(...)`、`repo:checkout(...)`、`repo:switch(...)`、`repo:fetch(...)` 和 `repo:push(...)` 这样的修改型操作都支持在其 options table 中传入 `confirm = true`，以便在执行动作前向用户请求确认。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:13
msgid "ptool.git.open"
msgstr "ptool.git.open"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:15
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:15"
msgid "`v0.6.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.6.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:17
msgid "`ptool.git.open(path?)` opens a repository directly and returns a `Repo` object."
msgstr "`ptool.git.open(path?)` 直接打开一个仓库，并返回 `Repo` 对象。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:20
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:20"
msgid "Arguments:"
msgstr "参数："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:22
msgid "`path` (string, optional): Repository path. If omitted, the current `ptool` runtime directory is used."
msgstr "`path`（string，可选）：仓库路径。省略时使用当前 `ptool` 运行时目录。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:25
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:25"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:27
msgid "Relative paths are resolved from the current `ptool` runtime directory, so they follow `ptool.cd(...)`."
msgstr "相对路径会从当前 `ptool` 运行时目录解析，因此会跟随 `ptool.cd(...)`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:29
msgid "This does not search parent directories. Use `ptool.git.discover(...)` when you want repository discovery behavior."
msgstr "这个 API 不会向父目录继续搜索仓库。如果你需要仓库发现行为，请使用 `ptool.git.discover(...)`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:32
