msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:118"
msgid "`v0.6.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.6.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:120
msgid "`Repo` represents an open Git repository handle returned by `ptool.git.open()`, `ptool.git.discover()`, or `ptool.git.clone()`."
msgstr "`Repo` 表示一个打开中的 Git 仓库句柄，由 `ptool.git.open()`、`ptool.git.discover()` 或 `ptool.git.clone()` 返回。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:123
msgid "It is implemented as a Lua userdata."
msgstr "它实现为 Lua userdata。"

